  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0bb2\u0b95\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b93\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b9e\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "World countries should consider Sri Lanka as a warning signal - IMF executive",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kristalina Georgieva, Managing Director of the International Monetary Fund, said that the economic crisis that Sri Lanka is currently facing is a warning signal to the rest of the world.",
        "Kristalina Georgieva said the above in an address in the presence of G-20 finance ministers and central bank governors in Indonesia.",
        "He further pointed out that the global economic situation in particular is significantly under crisis and volatility is relatively high.",
        "\"The threats already warned by the International Monetary Fund have now become real,\" said Kristalina Georgieva, who has expressed concern and said that the war situation in Ukraine has put excessive pressure on the prices of commodities, including food.",
        "'The crises that the world is currently facing may continue or intensify. In particular, the increase in inflation has the potential to have a massive impact on the economic growth of developing countries. Countries with high debt and limited policies are likely to suffer more. It is noteworthy that he pointed out that Sri Lanka should be considered as a warning signal in this regard."
      ],
